classes.name: Calculator
classes.docstring: Calculator class that provides basic mathematical operations

methods.name: add
methods.docstring:
Calculate the sum of two numbers

Args:
    a (int/float): First number
    b (int/float): Second number

Returns:
    int/float: Sum of the two numbers

methods.name: subtract
methods.docstring:
Calculate the difference of two numbers

Args:
    a (int/float): Minuend
    b (int/float): Subtrahend

Returns:
    int/float: Difference of the two numbers

methods.name: multiply
methods.docstring:
Calculate the product of two numbers

Args:
    a (int/float): First number
    b (int/float): Second number

Returns:
    int/float: Product of the two numbers

methods.name: divide
methods.docstring:
Calculate the quotient of two numbers

Args:
    a (int/float): Dividend
    b (int/float): Divisor

Returns:
    float: Quotient of the two numbers

Raises:
    ValueError: When divisor is zero
